# CODEOWNERS — pinned reviewer surface for pilotspry-maker/Atlas-Passport
#
# Purpose: prevent bot / AI coworker (Dispatch) or leaked tokens from
# self-merging changes to main. Combined with:
#   - required_approving_review_count = 1
#   - require_code_owner_reviews = true
#   - restrictions.users = ["pilotspry-maker"] on main
# this forces a human review by @pilotspry-maker for every PR touching
# the paths below.
#
# See docs/ops/branch_protection_plan.md for the full plan.
# See docs/dispatch_runbook.md §4 / §6 for the policy this enforces.

# Default owner — every file in the repo requires @pilotspry-maker review.
*                                       @pilotspry-maker

# High-sensitivity paths (redundant with * but explicit for clarity;
# also so any future entry above them can't accidentally remove
# ownership on these paths).
/supabase/migrations/**                 @pilotspry-maker
/.github/workflows/**                   @pilotspry-maker
/.github/CODEOWNERS                     @pilotspry-maker
/.github/branch-protection.expected.json @pilotspry-maker
/.github/branch-protection.baseline.json @pilotspry-maker
/docs/dispatch_runbook.md               @pilotspry-maker
/docs/ops/branch_protection_plan.md     @pilotspry-maker
/CLAUDE.md                              @pilotspry-maker
/scripts/ops/**                         @pilotspry-maker
